high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the small black end table.
Pick up the leftmost red credit card off of the end table.
Turn right to face the black desk.
Put the red credit card on the front edge of the black desk in front of the chair.
Turn left to face the small black end table again.
Pick up the red credit card off of the end table.
Turn right to face the black desk again.
Put the red credit card on the front edge of the black desk to the right of the card that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two red credit cards to a black desk.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the small stand to the right of the bookshelf.
Pick up the credit card that's in front of you on top of the stand to the left of the other credit card..
Turn right to face the desk.
Put then card on the desk in front of the black chair.
Turn back to your left to face the small stand again.
Pick up the other credit card that's on top of the stand.
Turn back to your right to  face the desk again.
Put this credit card to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the desk.

high_descs: Turn and go to the shelf to the right of the book shelf.
Pick up the credit card that is on the top shelf on the left side.
With the credit card in hand turn to your left and face the desk
Place the credit card on the front part of the desk right in front of the chair.
Turn to your left and face the shelf that is to the right of the book shelf.
Pick up the other credit card that is on the top shelf.
Turn to your right and face the desk with the credit card in hand.
Place the credit card to the right of the credit card that is in front of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the desk.
